<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Data Entry, Graphics Design, Guest Post Writing Portfolio">
    <title>My Services</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        h1, h2 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }
        .service-list {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .service-item {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 30%;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .service-item h3 {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .service-item a {
            display: block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007BFF;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .service-item a:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>My Services</h1>
</header>

<div class="container">
    <h2>What I Offer</h2>
    <p>I provide professional services in Data Entry, Graphic Design, and Guest Post Writing. Below are links to my profiles where you can explore my work further.</p>
    
    <div class="service-list">
        <div class="service-item">
            <h3>Fiverr</h3>
            <p>Check out my Fiverr profile for Data Entry and Graphic Design services.</p>
            <a href="https://www.fiverr.com/yourusername" target="_blank">Visit Fiverr</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="service-item">
            <h3>Upwork</h3>
            <p>Explore my Upwork portfolio for Guest Posting and other services.</p>
            <a href="https://www.upwork.com/freelancers/yourusername" target="_blank">Visit Upwork</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="service-item">
            <h3>Behance</h3>
            <p>Take a look at my graphic design portfolio on Behance.</p>
            <a href="https://www.behance.net/yourusername" target="_blank">Visit Behance</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; 2024 Your Name. All rights reserved.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
